Can be `const`. Also, this code was not immediately obvious to me, so I think a comment (and shorter lines) would be nice. 
```suggestion
                // Cost of a change output = (size of output * this tx feerate) + (size of spending input * discard feerate)
                const CAmount cost_of_change = GetDiscardRate(*this).GetFee(coin_selection_params.change_spend_size) 
                      + coin_selection_params.m_effective_feerate.GetFee(coin_selection_params.change_output_size);
```

